<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.9">
<l>valaṅkā tiṉmēltōṉ ṟippū vaṇintu</l>
<l rend="indent">mallikai vaṉamālai mauval mālai</l>
<l>ciliṅkārat tālkuḻal tāḻa viṭṭut</l>
<l rend="indent">tīṅkuḻal vāymaṭut tūti yūti</l>
<l>alaṅkārat tālvaru māyap piḷḷai</l>
<l rend="indent">yaḻakukaṇ ṭeṉmaka ḷācaip paṭṭu</l>
<l>vilaṅkinil lātetir niṉṟu kaṇṭīr</l>
<l rend="indent">veḷvaḷai kaḻaṉṟumeym melikiṉ ṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[When] my girl saw the beauty of the herder boy who came with a flourish—</l>
<l rend="indent">adorned with forest jasmine garlands and wild jasmine garlands,</l>
<l rend="indent">having placed a malabar lily blossom on [his] right ear,</l>
<l rend="indent">with [his] curly hair hanging low as decoration,</l>
<l rend="indent">holding [his] sweet flute to [his] lips, playing and playing—</l>
<l>desire arising [in her],</l>
<l>you saw [her] blocking [him], not remaining still,</l>
<l rend="indent">standing face-to-face [with him].</l>
<l>[Her] white bangles have become loose [and her] body becomes thin.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
